Plex Plugin for teleboy.ch
==========================

This plugin allows you to watch live TV in Switerland.

In order to use this plugin:
* install this plugin to ~/Library/Appliation Support/Plex Media Server/Plug-ins
* go to "http://www.teleboy.ch" in Safari
* register and log in
* start Plex and browse to the plugin
* enter your login data in the preferences inside the plugin


HOW TO FIX THE LOGOS (Pixelmator)
---------------------------------

For black logos:
* duplicate layer
* set brightness of the background to max. (white)
* apply filter: gaussian blur 16px

For white logos:
* duplicate layer
* set brightness of the background to min. (black)
* apply filter: gaussian blur 16px
